      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">knives or blades for planers and jointers <class-ref scheme="cpc">B27C1/00</class-ref></paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Woodworking machines used to produce a flat surface along a board&apos;s length (jointer or planer)</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">with rotating or non-rotating tools</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">with tools having a rotational vector which is perpendicular to the working surface <class-ref scheme="cpc">B27C1/005</class-ref></paragraph-text>
