            <table-column preferred-width="10.77cm">
              <paragraph-text type="body">Accessories fitted to machine tools for keeping tools or parts of the machine in good working condition or for cooling work; Safety devices specially combined with or arranged in, or specially adapted for use in connection with, machine tools</paragraph-text>
