<definition-item date-revised="2015-03-01"><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">B27C7/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Wood-turning machines; Equipment therefor  (<class-ref scheme="cpc">B23B</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">B23G</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">B23Q</class-ref>, take precedence; features of copying devices <class-ref scheme="cpc">B23Q35/00</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement>
