<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">B27C9/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Multi-purpose machines; Universal machines; Equipment therefor</definition-title><definition-statement>
      <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Machines that are useful for many purposes, e.g., convertible machines (machines that cannot be defined by the tool used if they have one or more spindles in which tools of different categories can be inserted, i.e drill or mill or saw etc., thus designed for performing more than one operation) and machines which carry out multiple operations whether the same or different.</paragraph-text>
